\f1\b What user inputs these functions need
\f0\b0                      \
                                                                                \
  Only two, and both are simple:\
  - \cf10 ski_date\cf3  \'97 \cf10 "YYYY-MM-DD"\cf3 , first day on the mountain                          \
  - \cf10 ability\cf3  \'97 one string: \cf10 "beginner"\cf3 , \cf10 "intermediate"\cf3 , \cf10 "advanced"\cf3 , or \cf10 "expert"\cf3    \
                                                                             \
  Everything else (coordinates, resort data) comes from \cf10 resorts.csv\cf3 .            \
                                                                                \
