\
  The coloring works by checking each GraphHopper waypoint for any CDOT\
  condition within ~3.5 miles, assigning the highest risk at that point, then\
  grouping consecutive same-risk waypoints into separate polylines. The segments\
   share their endpoint so the line looks continuous with no gaps.\
