   \cf10 additional_data\cf3  before keyword matching. CDOT's \cf10 condition_type\cf3  field contains\
   internal codes that can include words like "closed" even for non-closure\
  conditions. Run this in R to see exactly what's triggering it:\
\
  text <- tolower(paste(result$filtered_df$condition_type,\
