  Paste the output and I'll know exactly what to fix. My suspicion is it's a\
  \cf10 condition_type\cf3  code containing "closed" rather than an actual road closure in\
  the description text \'97 in which case the fix is to only match \cf10 CLOSURE_KEYWORDS\cf3 \
   against \cf10 additional_data\cf3 , not \cf10 condition_type\cf3 .\
